    {
        "content": "<p>No.</p>",
        "id": 193712239,
        "sender_full_name": "Reid Barton",
        "timestamp": 1586696450
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I was going to comment on it earlier, but as far as I can tell it's the picture for the bors github user and so we couldn't change it.</p>",
        "id": 193712254,
        "sender_full_name": "Reid Barton",
        "timestamp": 1586696491
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>What is the creepy part?  The unnecessarily large heading?  The name of the bot?  The logo?</p>",
        "id": 193712345,
        "sender_full_name": "Gabriel Ebner",
        "timestamp": 1586696588
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>For me mainly the logo, I don't know what bors is.</p>",
        "id": 193712416,
        "sender_full_name": "Reid Barton",
        "timestamp": 1586696697
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Other than this bot, I mean</p>",
        "id": 193712420,
        "sender_full_name": "Reid Barton",
        "timestamp": 1586696711
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I always thought it's a Russian name, but I guess I mixed it up with Boris.  This is the official explanation for the name:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>It’s a reference to a 1953 sci-fi novel 17 about the robot, Bors, that ran the world’s last surviving government.</p>\n</blockquote>",
        "id": 193712599,
        "sender_full_name": "Gabriel Ebner",
        "timestamp": 1586696900
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Now that you mentioned it, the font is unnecessarily large as well</p>",
        "id": 193712680,
        "sender_full_name": "Reid Barton",
        "timestamp": 1586697078
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>The <code>bors-ng</code> project is reasonably active.  You could submit a PR to change the font size.</p>",
        "id": 193714571,
        "sender_full_name": "Gabriel Ebner",
        "timestamp": 1586700387
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>If anybody wants to test changes on a live bors instance, I've set up a personal bors here: <a href=\"https://borslein.herokuapp.com/\" title=\"https://borslein.herokuapp.com/\">https://borslein.herokuapp.com/</a>  This is deployed from by bors-ng fork, feel free to submit a PR if you want to test something: <a href=\"https://github.com/gebner/bors-ng\" title=\"https://github.com/gebner/bors-ng\">https://github.com/gebner/bors-ng</a><br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/j1vBK2hyxNh3sU31BtoPr0so/borslein.png\" title=\"borslein.png\">borslein.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/j1vBK2hyxNh3sU31BtoPr0so/borslein.png\" title=\"borslein.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/3121/j1vBK2hyxNh3sU31BtoPr0so/borslein.png\"></a></div>",
        "id": 193714644,
        "sender_full_name": "Gabriel Ebner",
        "timestamp": 1586700534
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>An alternative approach is for us all to start using that size font, so it's less obvious that bors is being so loud.</p>",
        "id": 193714646,
        "sender_full_name": "Kevin Buzzard",
        "timestamp": 1586700536
    },
