        "sender_full_name": "Patrick Massot",
        "timestamp": 1586853758
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>No, it's hosted on the free tier of heroku (a cloud hosting service).  Sometimes it takes a few seconds to load the <a href=\"https://borslein.herokuapp.com\" title=\"https://borslein.herokuapp.com\">https://borslein.herokuapp.com</a> page, but I don't think this causes any problems for <code>bors r+</code> comments and such.</p>",
